{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"userId"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"emails:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"emails"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"kind":"text","text":")("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier."}]}],"name":"userId"},{"name":"emails","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Atomically associates a user ID with multiple email addresses and provides","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"confirmation when the operation completes. This is the recommended method","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for user identification during authentication flows."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle OAuth login with full user setup:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class OAuthLoginHandler {","","    func handleOAuthCallback(_ authResult: OAuthResult,","                            completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","","        \/\/ Extract user info from OAuth result","        let userId = authResult.userId","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primaryEmail = authResult.email {","            emails.append(primaryEmail)","        }","        if let verifiedEmails = authResult.verifiedEmails {","            emails.append(contentsOf: verifiedEmails.filter { $0 != authResult.email })","        }","","        \/\/ Set user and emails with confirmation","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUser(userId, emails: emails) { error in","            if let error = error {","                Logger.error(\"User setup failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                completion(.failure(error))","                return","            }","","            \/\/ User is now fully identified - set profile tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"oauth_provider\": authResult.provider.rawValue,","                \"has_profile_picture\": authResult.profilePictureURL != nil,","                \"locale\": authResult.locale ?? Locale.current.identifier,","                \"first_login\": !self.hasExistingSession(for: userId)","            ])","","            Analytics.track(\"oauth_login_complete\", properties: [","                \"provider\": authResult.provider.rawValue,","                \"email_count\": emails.count","            ])","","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","title":"setUser:emails:completion:","roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:completion:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUser:emails:completion:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:completion:"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user identifier and emails with completion handler."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:completion:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUser:emails:completion:":{"type":"topic","title":"setUser:emails:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUser:emails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:completion:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:completion:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user identifier and emails with completion handler."}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:completion:"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"}}}